sentences: Marjorie Merryman (born 1951) is an American composer, author, and music educator.
She is a member of the composition faculty at the Manhattan School of Music since 2007, where she also served as Interim President, Provost and Senior Vice President at Manhattan School of Music.

She has been the recipient of numerous awards, including two prizes from the American Academy of Arts and Letters, the Walter Hinrichsen Award, presented annually by American Academy of Arts and Letters and in 2014, the "Arts and Letters Award in Music: "This award is given in recognition of "â€¦.
